

<section id="about" style="padding: 60px 0; background-color: var(--gh-bg);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="about-card" style="background: var(--gh-canvas); border: 1px solid var(--gh-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px;">
            <MudGrid Spacing="6">
                <MudItem xs="12" md="6">
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.h5" Style="font-weight: 700; color: var(--gh-text); margin-bottom: 24px;">Professional Summary</MudText>
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Style="color: var(--gh-text-muted); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.1rem;">
                        I am a dedicated **Full-Stack .NET Software Developer** with over 5 years of professional experience. 
                        My expertise lies in building scalable, high-performance web and mobile applications using modern Microsoft technologies.
                    </MudText>
                    <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="mt-4" Style="color: var(--gh-text-muted); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.1rem;">
                        I am passionate about translating complex design requirements into elegant, maintainable code. 
                        Whether it's a responsive Blazor WebAssembly app or a cross-platform .NET MAUI solution, I focus on delivering quality and value.
                    </MudText>
                </MudItem>
                <MudItem xs="12" md="6">
                    <div style="background: var(--gh-bg); border: 1px solid var(--gh-border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; height: 100%;">
                        <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle1" Style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--gh-text); margin-bottom: 12px;">Technical Philosophy</MudText>
                        <MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Style="color: var(--gh-text-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
                            I believe in the power of **clean code** and **solid architecture**. 
                            My development process is centered around scalability, security, and a seamless user experience. 
                            I am a continuous learner, always exploring new ways to optimize workflows and leverage the latest framework features.
                        </MudText>
                    </div>
                </MudItem>
            </MudGrid>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    @@media (max-width: 992px) {
        .about-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
        }
    }
</style>
 